children.text: A compilation of performances from Enough Said spoken word series events held at Bistro 4 (4040 St. Laurent, Montreal, QC, H2W 1Y8, Canada) by Swifty Lazarus (Todd Swift and Tom Walsh), bill bissett, Sharon H. Nelson, Ian Stephens, Fortner Anderson, Robert Allen, Douglas Isaac, ga press (Colin Christie and Corey Frost), Ian Ferrier, Steve Luxton, and Raymond Filip.
